{"data": [{"id": "4743287", "title": "Qualitative And Contrarian Outlook For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Laughing couple with arms raised riding roller coaster at amusement park\" data-id=\"1083856232\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The market has had a good year in 2024, with the S&amp;P500 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500\u00ae ETF Trust\">SPY</a></span>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>) up +26.9% year to date, driven by technology stocks and the AI revolution. Some people say bubble, others say this time is different. Maybe, maybe</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743287-qualitative-and-contrarian-outlook-for-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:13:51"}, {"id": "4743303", "title": "Eurozone Bond Spreads: A Reordering In Progress", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"European flag in Frankfurt, Germany.\" data-id=\"1455668014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1157px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">littleclie</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2>Spread risks look more contained and idiosyncratic</h2> <p>The market seems to sense that eurozone risks are by now largely contained, and we are looking more at idiosyncratic country stories. The reaction of Bund swap spreads to episodes</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743303-eurozone-bond-spreads-reordering-progress", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:00:00"}, {"id": "4743302", "title": "ceo-john-stankey-at-ubs-global-media-and-communications-conference", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by AT&amp;T Inc. in conjunction with this event.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106097\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743302-ceo-john-stankey-ubs-global-media-and-communications-conference", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:51:10"}, {"id": "4743278", "title": "From Mergers To Margins: Capri's Struggle For A Turnaround", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Harrods de Heathrow\" data-id=\"471456887\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"761px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Maxian/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>A lot changed for Capri Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CPRI\" title=\"Capri Holdings Limited\">CPRI</a></span>) in the last few weeks. Capri and Tapestry (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TPR\" title=\"Tapestry, Inc.\">TPR</a>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4288973-capri-holdings-tapestry-agree-to-end-85b-merger-deal\">have terminated the merger agreement</a> due to regulatory objections, which left the company to pursue its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471456887/image_471456887.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743278-from-mergers-to-margins-capri-struggle-for-turnaround", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:42:38"}, {"id": "4743296", "title": "D-Market Elektronik Hizmetler ve Ticaret A.S. 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by D-Market Elektronik Hizmetler ve Ticaret A.S. in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106096\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743296-d-market-elektronik-hizmetler-ve-ticaret-s-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:38:24"}, {"id": "4743291", "title": "SSA Spreads Pushed Wider As Underlying Sovereign Levels Get Reassessed", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"United States Savings Bonds Series EE\" data-id=\"157672005\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1028px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">NoDerog</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2>SSAs face ongoing pressure from the underlying reassessment of sovereign risk</h2> <p>For supranational, sub-sovereign and agency (SSA) bonds, 2024 was, for a large part, a year of gradually widening spreads over swaps. This was mainly the effect of the European Central Bank continuing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157672005/image_157672005.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743291-ssa-spreads-pushed-wider-as-underlying-sovereign-levels-get-reassessed", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:35:00"}, {"id": "4743281", "title": "MongoDB Q3: Expect AI Workloads To Set Off Platform Consumption Next Year", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"MongoDB office in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1157051255\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction &amp; Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724811-mongodb-genai-paves-the-way-for-a-return-to-20-percent-revenue-growth-upgrade\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724811-mongodb-genai-paves-the-way-for-a-return-to-20-percent-revenue-growth-upgrade\" target=\"_blank\">last wrote</a> about MongoDB (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MDB\" title=\"MongoDB, Inc.\">MDB</a></span>) in October, where I upgraded my rating on the stock from a \u201chold\u201d to a \u201cbuy\u201d, as management had raised its FY25 guidance back to the level that it had set in its </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743281-mongodb-q3-expect-ai-workloads-to-set-off-platform-consumption-next-year", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4743288", "title": "Is The Downshift In U.S. Inflation Stalling?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Graphic on coin towers showing the rise in the price of fuel. Selective focus\" data-id=\"1368208490\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Francisco Javier Ortiz Marzo/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Disinflation has stalled recently, but economists are debating if this is a temporary blip that will soon give way to a softer trend. Tomorrow's consumer price report for November will be widely read for an</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368208490/image_1368208490.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743288-downshift-us-inflation-stalling", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:20:00"}, {"id": "4743094", "title": "If The Market Shut Down For 10 Years, I'd Be Happy To Own These 2 Stocks", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Top View of Pink Porcelain Piggy Bank with Metal Coins in Blue Triangle Maze\" data-id=\"2152354572\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">spawns/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Warren Buffett has many deep and thought-provoking quotes on investing. One of my favorite ones is the following:</p> <blockquote><p>Only buy something that you'd be perfectly happy to hold if the market shut down for 10 years.</p></blockquote> <p>The direct message of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743094-if-market-shut-down-for-10-years-id-be-happy-to-own-these-2-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:15:00"}, {"id": "4743284", "title": "Market Snakes Follow Ladders", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand-drawn game Snakes and Ladders. Close-up.\" data-id=\"1248963397\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">OlgaKhorkova</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Canada's Venture Composite Index (a basket of economically sensitive micro-cap companies, 44% weighted in materials, 30% information technology, 15.74% in energy, 3.5% health care, 2.48% financials, 1.85% industrials, .58% communication services, and .32% consumer discretionary) appears to concur with former BoC head Stephen Poloz's recessionary assessment.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743284-market-snakes-follow-ladders", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:10:00"}]}